        <headline>Heat Advisory issued August 13 at 9:57PM CDT until August 14 at 9:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Temperatures of 105 degrees.

* WHERE...Palo Duro Canyon.

* WHEN...From noon to 9 PM CDT Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures and high humidity may cause heat
illnesses.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Terrain features present in the canyon may
see temperatures exceed 105 degrees down near the canyon floor.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
